Package com.codecool.shop.model

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codecool.shop.model.BaseModel
      • com.codecool.shop.model.Product

  • public class Product
extends BaseModel
    This class serves as model for every product and holds all the information about each of them. It extends the BaseModel abstract class from which it inherits its base fields like id, name and description, to which four more class specific fields are added, the default price, default currency, product category and supplier
    Since:
    2018-01-20
